{"type":"text","timestamp":1775840326415,"sessionID":"ses_287ac3cbdffe8hzwjoSofINCzZ","part":{"id":"prt_d7854e922001vxgbyjkxpURgMU","messageID":"msg_d7854d997001vSpwxTVVE2Sn4P","sessionID":"ses_287ac3cbdffe8hzwjoSofINCzZ","type":"text","text":"I've written `proposal.md` for AR-003. The proposal covers:\n\n1. **Purpose** - Centralize common types, establish naming conventions, provide reusable validation\n2. **Scope** - What's in/out of scope for this change\n3. **Current State Analysis** - Documents existing shared types (`ResourceQuota`, `NetworkPolicy`, `LifecycleHook`, etc.) and constants (`AgentRuntimePhase*`, `AgentRuntimeCondition*`)\n4. **Proposed Changes**:\n   - Type categorization (shared vs. CRD-specific)\n   - Standardize naming (current naming is already good)\n   - Extract shared validation functions\n   - Add package documentation\n   - Plan for future CRD compatibility\n5. **Impact Analysis** - Low impact, backward compatible changes\n6. **Alternatives Considered** - Separate common package, use k8s core types, generate from schema\n7. **Implementation Checklist** - Concrete tasks to complete","time":{"start":1775840326413,"end":1775840326413}}}
